We recently deployed Service Desk to our organization. One of the issues that's really confused users is that every Service Desk notification they receive appears as though it came from them (i.e., Joe Reporter (helpdesk@mydomain.com), even though someone else on the Service Desk team might have caused it by adding a comment or changing a status.

It would be great if we could customize the FROM address to avoid this confusion.

