As an administrator of a service desk, I would like the ability to have the first CC'ed user made the assignee of an issue created via email.

The built-in JIRA "Create a new issue or add a comment to an existing issue" mail handler contains the CC Assignee option. This causes the first CC'ed user to become the assignee. 

This option is not available in the Service Desk Mail Handler which prevents the use of this feature. This would also add a roadblock if this option is currently used by a team migrating from a JIRA project to a JIRA service desk.

