If you create a new workflow, you will be able to change the name and description of this workflow by clicking the pencil icon beside the name
!Created.png|thumbnail!

When you create a new Service Desk project, a workflow for this project will be automatically generated with the name
{{JIRA Service Desk IT Support Workflow generated for Project SD}}
